Package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.metapath.item

Interface IRequiredValueModelNodeItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDefinitionNodeItem, IItem, IModelNodeItem, INodeContext, INodeItem, INodeItemVisitable, IPathSegment, IRequiredValueDefinitionNodeItem, IRequiredValueNodeItem
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IRequiredValueAssemblyNodeItem, IRequiredValueFieldNodeItem, IRootAssemblyNodeItem
    public interface IRequiredValueModelNodeItem
extends IModelNodeItem, IRequiredValueDefinitionNodeItem
    This marker interface indicates that the IModelNodeItem must have a value to exist.
